title: Dave Mtthews Band - Live Trax 45 (2018) [FLAC]
description: https://i.imgur.com/JVivSiN.jpg From the opening notes of Dreamgirl (the first time this song opened a show since 2005) all the way through the 20 min Two Step show closer, this performance from the Susquehanna Bank Center has something for every discerning DMB fan’s ear. The band always seems at home on the stage in Camden, NJ, treating the crowd with gems across their repertoire - from the intimate Belly Full to the fully rocking cover of Led Zeppelin’s Good Times Bad Times. All in all, this show is a mix of old and new, with an energetic crowd taking in some fantastic performances. Tracklist: 1. Dreamgirl 2. Drive In, Drive Out 3. Joyride 4. What Would You Say 5. Crush 6. JTR 7. Good Times Bad Times 8. #41 9. Kill the Preacher 10. Why I Am 11. Help Myself 12. Mercy 13. So Much To Say 14. Drunken Soldier 15. Hunger For the Great Light 16. Belly Full 17. Typical Situation 18. Ants Marching 19. Halloween 20. Oh 21. Lie In Our Graves 22. Pig 23. Two Step
